{"type": "article", "id": 23529, "title": "编织家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104150cKya7X8RBqjzf6wg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套编织家具来自纽约女设计师 Kate Casey，她成立了独立工作室 PEG WOODWORKING。座位和椅背上是她自己用棉线手工编织的图案，经过交叉和重叠之后形成了丰富的几何图形。有些通过不同颜色做区分，有些仅仅依靠疏密表现了深浅和光泽。这是设计师的工作室和<a href=\"http://www.pegwoodworking.com/new-products/\">购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104148nDGopWght5PvIHKB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104149VQklwibPDmSNKAM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071041492reTjmQKEN1ix5tC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104149Yi0ezjwfFPBodEhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710415058bjNYTKrQ9x2g36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}